categories: Category:Jedi trainees of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: T'boor was a senior male Jedi Padawan who was enrolled in the Jedi Order's academy on Coruscant.

Brought to the Temple at a young age, T'boor was selected by a Jedi Master before the Clone Wars. Soon after the Battle of Kothlis, T'boor joined a fellow Padawan Ahsoka Tano as part of Green team in a competition arranged by Master Taria Damsin. The competition, taking place in the new Sublevel Nineteen Training Dojo, ended in a tie. Sadly T'boor fell in battle against modified B1-Series battle droids as the Green team crossed the dojo's river.
